content: As an AI language model, I don't have personal beliefs or feelings but based on observations and studies, the message of consequences of selfish actions is a common theme that resonates with audiences across different cultures and backgrounds. Many people can relate to the negative impact that selfish behavior can have on relationships and the importance of considering others in our actions. Thus, the message of empathy and selflessness in "Into the Woods" is likely to resonate with audiences and encourage them to reflect on their own behavior in relationships.
